SEARCH
Package br.com.concepting.framework.audit.annotations

Annotation Interface Auditable

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({TYPE,METHOD,FIELD}) public @interface Auditable
Class that defines the auditing's annotation. This should be used in methods or classes to enable the auditing.
